172
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:08,959
I need to have my own engineering team.

173
00:13:08,959 --> 00:13:11,040
I'm going to make sure I run my own silo.

174
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:17,440
And if you're a $40 billion business in product revenues, 45 billion, whatever um um we were at the time,

175
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:27,040
um and and then all of a sudden your goal is that you're going to just run a bunch of $40 million businesses and break it up into a series of $40

