00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:40,720
And we did this about five five and a half years ago which when I first joined this was a very deliberate decision which was we cannot operate in a walled garden.

194
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:51,519
We have to make sure that we operate in an open ecosystem which means we have to be completely comfortable with having a competitor that we're going to partner with

